Not true.. Bards get Two Hand Blunt (1).. Enough for us to wield it. When using the OT Hammer having a lower skill helps us more then lets say a Monk with a 2HB(252).. You can proc even on a miss and while attacking greens to proc a Monk is going to kill a few before procing were a Bard will miss a lot and not do much damage.. 
<br />

<br />
Plus proc rate it on it's own timer so the delay of this weapon doesn't effect it in any way.</span></td>
